      <title>随着夏季高温加剧，南方正在采取相应措施，确保儿童安全</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/21/nx-s1-5015094/the-south-is-adapting-to-help-keep-kids-safe-as-summer-heat-intensifies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着气候变化导致热浪持续时间更长、强度更大，户外玩耍现在变得危险。路易斯安那州的营地正在做出调整，以应对今年夏天更高的气温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/21/nx-s1-5015094/the-south-is-adapting-to-help-keep-kids-safe-as-summer-heat-intensifies</guid>
